N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 146.3 - Annual Financial Report

State Regulations

If an Annual Financial Report delivered to the Department of

State for filing complies as to form with the requirements of law and the
filing fee required by law for such report has been paid, the report shall be
filed by the Department of State. Notes
